# Implementation Plan - Cups Page and Schedule Fix

The user reported that the accelerated cup scheduling (July-only, Mon/Wed/Fri) did not work and requested a new "Cups" page under Playoffs.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> - **Database Wipe**: I will wipe all existing cup data to ensure the new generation logic (Copa Italia, July schedule) can run without being blocked by old entries.
> - **Navigation**: A new "Cups" link will be added to the sidebar.
> - **Bracket View**: The new page will visualize the Copa Italia knockout bracket.

## Proposed Changes

### Database Cleanup

#### [NEW] [wipe-cups.js](file:///c:/Users/wobin/Documents/GitHub/VBM/tmp/wipe-cups.js)
- A script to TRUNCATE `cup_competitions`, `cup_rounds`, and `cup_fixtures`.

### API Layer

#### [NEW] [src/app/api/cups/route.ts](file:///c:/Users/wobin/Documents/GitHub/VBM/src/app/api/cups/route.ts)
- GET handler to fetch the active National Cup (Copa Italia) for the current year, including its rounds and fixtures.

### UI Layer

#### [MODIFY] [src/components/sidebar.tsx](file:///c:/Users/wobin/Documents/GitHub/VBM/src/components/sidebar.tsx)
- Add a new navigation item for **Cups** (using the `Trophy` icon).

#### [NEW] [src/app/cups/page.tsx](file:///c:/Users/wobin/Documents/GitHub/VBM/src/app/cups/page.tsx)
- Implementation of the Cups visualization page.
- Features:
    - Round-by-round knockout bracket display.
    - Status indicators (Scheduled, Live, Completed).
    - Match results.

## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
- Run `node tmp/wipe-cups.js`.
- Manually trigger `POST /api/proceed-to-playoffs` (or advance past June 30).
- Verify `Copa Italia` is generated with the 1-month July schedule.

### Manual Verification
- Navigate to the new `/cups` page.
- Confirm the 2-tier entry (R1 North/South, R2 Premier entry) is visually represented.
- Confirm matchdates are Mon/Wed/Fri in July.
